{"tid":1712773,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"雖然多謝說話、物資都重要，但班中學生大學生，最想要既其實係人","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T15:31:22.000Z","uid":161430,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f095d84bd2ac97d720a04d64f4c54017be528ce","tid":1712773,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"想你一齊陪佢奮鬥，佢就唔駛咁辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n想你聽朝一齊三罷，幫手罷，<br />\n比起去去返工既你，同佢講「多謝」，更有用。<br />\n<br />\n想你講一句「我黎幫手喇」「我地一齊上」，<br />\n好過大大聲叫「放人！」「點解香港變成咁架」。<br />\n<br />\n一個人罷工冇用，如果一間公司得一個人罷工，<br />\n果個人簡直係異類，仲可能比人炒都似，<br />\n但一間公司只有一個人唔罷工，咁唔罷果個先係傻鳩。<br />\n<br />\n一幾個人去行動，咁果幾個人就係去送頭比對家，<br />\n但係一千人一萬人行動，咁送頭果個就係對家。<br />\n<br />\n聽朝你願唔願意，比最想要既野比班學生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6ef853abeaf25d105b673dc850ff05e9fa2f94d","tid":1712773,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477adf20b2ff39cc5cb00fc5e55f4ae09aec65cd","tid":1712773,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae39719214e2cf8c9e8676d292f5785628e34b3","tid":1712773,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:23:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692482263b559d2a67ab02ee104005b770ed943d","tid":1712773,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"聽日要既唔係乜野，係人"},{"pid":"2bea58c3eb74050a9b21df594bc4a47dd13a826c","tid":1712773,"uid":178214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"push"}]}